title: 🎒 "The purpose of education is to replace an empty mind with an open one." - Malcolm Forbes
content:
Given an integer n, return true if n^3 and n have the same set of digits.

Example:

$ sameDigits(1) // true
$ sameDigits(10) // true
$ sameDigits(251894) // true
$ sameDigits(251895) // false
